sourceCode.pages/Search/index.axml:
<container title="搜索下拉">
  <input
    placeholder="请输入内容"
    onChange="onChange"
    className="search-bar {{value ? '' : 'search-bar-radius'}}"
    confirm-type="search"
    allowClear
    focus
    onConfirm="onConfirm"
  >
    <icon slot="prefix" type="SearchOutline" />
  </input>
  
  <scroll-view scroll-y="{{true}}" class="search-recommend" a:if="{{value}}">
    <view a:if="{{loading}}" class="search-loading">
      <loading color="#1677ff" />
    </view>
    <view a:else a:for="{{ searchRecommendList }}" class="search-recommend-item" data-index="{{index}}" onTap="onTap">
      <icon type="SearchOutline" class="search-recommend-item-icon"/>{{item}}
    </view>
    
  </scroll-view>

</container>
sourceCode.pages/Select/index.axml:
<list-item>
  选择城市
  <picker
    slot="extra"
    onOk="onOk"
    onVisibleChange="onVisibleChange"
    onCancel="onCancel"
    value="{{value}}"
    placeholder="请选择"
    title="请选择"
    options="{{list}}">

    <view slot="title">
      <input
        placeholder="请输入内容"
        onChange="onChange"
        confirm-type="search"
        allowClear
      >
        <icon slot="prefix" type="SearchOutline" />
      </input>
    </view>
  </picker>
</list-item>
